verse.lines:
{lang-eng}I am not skilled to understand
What God hath willed, what God hath planned;
I only know at His right hand
Stands One who is my Savior.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}I take Him at His word indeed:
“Christ died for sinners”—this I read;
For in my heart I find a need
Of Him to be my Savior!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}And was there then no other way
For God to take? - I cannot say;
I only bless Him, day by day,
Who saved me through my Saviour.{/lang-eng}
